{"tid":905204,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"[執衫] 點樣處理已經唔著嘅衫？","createTime":"2018-11-17T03:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T13:27:33.000Z","uid":55296,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d6eaff9798bd19d7e15d11b296d035f18cb47611","tid":905204,"uid":55296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"年尾轉季開始清衫櫃，有啲衫因為人生階段唔同咗已經唔再著，但都幾新淨嘅，各位會點處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過擺上二手app 賣，擺到出年都仲喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 亦試過改做袋呀狗仔衫，幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲真係超級新淨嘅拎過比一間專寄賣二手女人同小朋友衫嘅社企，佢話賣唔出就會捐比有需要嘅人，但試過幾次閪到唔想再去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最終都係拎去救世軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea64c77b4c2a365414078be8809af5bd0ad44dd8","tid":905204,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":27,"score":-24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd3c9cd98c66ec58a5508942a93442e7838ee134","tid":905204,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:12:02.000Z","msg":"都係捐左去, 上網好少有人買"},{"pid":"df9f7ebc0e869668dde28a0113aa627f48367480","tid":905204,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:14:45.000Z","msg":"有同樣煩惱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好多衫幾年無著，塞住哂個衣櫃"},{"pid":"3f2b2ff80e8c931c658b75f3d373cf500f216b83","tid":905204,"uid":172024,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:22:08.000Z","msg":"可以放入衣物回收箱呀"},{"pid":"139e8adac7c7004fa6d98428fb03d9ec0ea3dad8","tid":905204,"uid":47020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T04:23:29.000Z","msg":"放落樓下個回收箱"},{"pid":"522a5665c093c6e2a376f8217d3cbcea864bbd28","tid":905204,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re